Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.96,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(369,366)}Resurrection
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that you're dealing with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under no circumstances should you let him see your face, and exercise extreme caution while restraining him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, if Higuchi makes even one suspicious move...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll immobilize him without actually killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'll immobilize him without actually killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, did you bring something to obscure your face with?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.81,0:00:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! {\alpha&HFF&}Thank you very much, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! Thank you very much, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi, put both hands up and step out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi-san, as we planned, place the transceiver on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi, {\alpha&HFF&}how were you killing people? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi, how were you killing people? {\alpha&HFF&}Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi, how were you killing people? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, we'll make you confess using any means at our disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably won't believe me, but if you write the name of a person whose face you know in that notebook, that person will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I've found it in his bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true there are names written here, {\alpha&HFF&}but there's nothing unusual about this note--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true there are names written here, but there's nothing unusual about this note--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yagami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}Monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami-san, you aren't carrying a gun at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Yagami-san, you aren't carrying a gun at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}Mogi! Can't you see that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mogi! {\alpha&HFF&}Can't you see that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mogi! Can't you see that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, you're very tired at the moment--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening, Mogi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}Ah... I-It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... {\alpha&HFF&}I-It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... I-{\alpha&HFF&}It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... I-It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... {\alpha&HFF&}this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... I-It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please bring that notebook to the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you possibly be planning, Yagami Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By touching a Death Note that you previously owned, {\alpha&HFF&}all your memories associated with it will be recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By touching a Death Note that you previously owned, all your memories associated with it will be recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a Shinigami... {\alpha&HFF&}they really do... exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a Shinigami... they really do... {\alpha&HFF&}exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a Shinigami... they really do... exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Showed each other our notebooks in Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love at first sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, give me the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's method of killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira... the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two notebooks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than one notebook exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am L...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am L...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}Are you okay? Anyone would be petrified if they saw that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay? {\alpha&HFF&}Anyone would be petrified if they saw that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay? Anyone would be petrified if they saw that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, we've got to compare the names written here against the list of victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... {\alpha&HFF&}yes... I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... yes... {\alpha&HFF&}I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... yes... I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relinquishing all ownership of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ownership of this notebook now returns to Rem. {\alpha&HFF&}Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ownership of this notebook now returns to Rem. Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. {\alpha&HFF&}Your point being?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Your point being?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now give that notebook to Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner of this notebook is now Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, next, I want you to drop that notebook here, onto the ground of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, guess it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the ownership returns to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the ownership has gone round in a circle; nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there'll be a time when this will be of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the first notebook that I received from Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving it back to you, and I want you to give it to Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I'll need you to pass that to someone who has a reasonably high status, yet remains greedy for success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who'll undoubtedly use the notebook to further those goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this will guarantee Misa's release from imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she still hasn't been released after several years, kill me. {\alpha&HFF&}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she still hasn't been released after several years, kill me. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, {\alpha&HFF&}what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all to save Misa. {\alpha&HFF&}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all to save Misa. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood... {\alpha&HFF&}if this will help Misa, I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood... if this will help Misa, I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'll manipulate the situation so, like Misa, I'll be detained and under 24-hour surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While in detention, I'll relinquish all ownership of the Death Note and it'll erase any associated memories I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, the judging of criminals will recommence, and if that continues, at some stage, Ryuuzaki will be forced to release us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, with my memories gone, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sure I'll attempt to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, with my memories gone, I'm sure I'll attempt to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the type of person I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you plan to find the person Rem gives the notebook to before L can, and reclaim the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. {\alpha&HFF&}And I'll kill whoever has ownership of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. And I'll kill whoever has ownership of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one problem:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hold no ownership over that Death Note, your memories will only return as long as you're physically touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you let go, all your memories will be erased once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to kill Higuchi without letting go of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, the ownership will pass to me, and my memories won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pull this four times with less than a second between each...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success! {\alpha&HFF&}I knew I'd be wearing this at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success! I knew I'd be wearing this at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old habits die hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, please escort Higuchi to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-{\alpha&HFF&}Okay... understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay... {\alpha&HFF&}understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay... understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}if analyzed scientifically, I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook... if analyzed scientifically, {\alpha&HFF&}I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook... if analyzed scientifically, I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, that's not like you. {\alpha&HFF&}That thing is beyond science.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, that's not like you. That thing is beyond science.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the longest 40 seconds of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi! {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki! Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi! Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi! Ryuuzaki! Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Higuchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, father?! {\alpha&HFF&}If Higuchi dies now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, father?! If Higuchi dies now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}This isn't possible... but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't possible... {\alpha&HFF&}but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't possible... but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, {\alpha&HFF&}he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next, Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next, Ryuuzaki... will be you.
Comment: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How to use"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:10:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The human whose name is written in this note shall die."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This note will not take effect unless the writer has the person's face in their mind when they write his/her name."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Therefore, people sharing the same name will not be affected."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is written within 40 seconds of writing the person's name, it will happen as it is written."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is not specified, by default, the person will die of a heart attack."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes and 40 seconds are granted to write any further details."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, in the "How to use"-section at the back, it states:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you make this note unusable by tearing it up or burning it, all the humans who have touched the note till then will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}Is that true, Aizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is that true, Aizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.69,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, it's written right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that while that rule exists, they won't destroy the notebook, and there's no danger of me losing my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.47,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw.. that's just shit... why didn't you tell me this earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I won't get in trouble with the old man for writing in fake rules, will I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are no rules regarding that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then. {\alpha&HFF&}But Light, I'm counting on you for more apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then. But Light, I'm counting on you for more apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have said "I want to see the Shinigami too", and touched that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't, you'd be the only one in the investigation not knowing what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I want to be on the same level as everyone else in this investigation. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this final sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the person using the note fails to continuously write names of people to be killed within 13 days of each other, then the user will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! {\alpha&HFF&}This means that both Light-kun and Misa-Misa are completely cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This means that both Light-kun and Misa-Misa are completely cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun and Amane were imprisoned for over 50 days, and even now are under surveillance. {\alpha&HFF&}If either were Kira, they'd no longer be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun and Amane were imprisoned for over 50 days, and even now are under surveillance. If either were Kira, they'd no longer be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great news, isn't it, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem-san... {\alpha&HFF&}wasn't it? The white person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem-san... wasn't it? The white person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, that's rude! You can't go around calling them "white".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other Death Notes in the human world, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure. Maybe there are, maybe there aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If other notebooks did exist, {\alpha&HFF&}would the rules be the same for all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If other notebooks did exist, would the rules be the same for all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Ryuuzaki. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way that Rem will let you cast doubt upon these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Ryuuzaki. There's no way that Rem will let you cast doubt upon these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they'd be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many notebooks within the world of Shinigami, but the rules are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those notebooks under human possession also share a common set of rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}the suspicions surrounding Light-kun and Amane have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, the suspicions surrounding Light-kun and Amane have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to end their surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, it's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for everything up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the case is still far from solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although these handcuffs will be removed, I'll continue to investigate from here, if that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Misa and I are 100% clear of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules written by a Shinigami in a Death Note... {\alpha&HFF&}you'd have to believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules written by a Shinigami in a Death Note... you'd have to believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the fake rules I created, Ryuuzaki has nowhere to go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand this Ryuuzaki: {\alpha&HFF&}in any world, rules are something that are made by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand this Ryuuzaki: in any world, rules are something that are made by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will bow down to the rules I've created.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to oppose me, the new god of this world, and for your transgression, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Promise me that you'll text me every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that I finally have to part with Misa-Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Matsuda, leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can be seen on the security cameras, from this angle, they shouldn't be able to see my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, when you're certain that no one else is around, I want you to go to the place I'm about to tell you and dig up something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Your memories have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Misa will do good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I remember! {\alpha&HFF&}Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I remember! Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I remember! Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, if you're reading this, it's likely that your memory has been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember a friend of mine, from Todai University, who introduced himself as "Ryuuga Hideki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to write his real name in this notebook and bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as soon as possible, burn this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take only a few pages from the notebook, and re-bury the notebook itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you see me, touch me with a piece of paper from this notebook as naturally as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can obey me in all this... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll love you, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can obey me in all this... I'll love you, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}________________________{\alpha&H00&}...love you, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This is all Light's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... {\alpha&HFF&}and kill Ryuuga Hideki... Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... and kill Ryuuga Hideki... {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... and kill Ryuuga Hideki... Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should remove another obstacle for Light, and I'll have helped him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Light. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Light. I can't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to see tens, hundreds of names and lifespans every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can remember! {\alpha&HFF&}Stupid Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can remember! Stupid Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk! It's so good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, sorry but... {\alpha&HFF&}being male and all that... that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, sorry but... being male and all that... {\alpha&HFF&}that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, sorry but... being male and all that... that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light told me to bring it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Apples in the human world are... how d'ya say it? "Juicy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, they're damned good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna try eating one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an apple from the world of Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look very tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Ryuk. {\alpha&HFF&}I want to trade eyes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Ryuk. I want to trade eyes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna make a deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize that you've already made a deal with Rem once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your remaining lifespan has already been halved once; {\alpha&HFF&}you sure you wanna do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your remaining lifespan has already been halved once; you sure you wanna do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've completely forgotten the one name that I needed to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light will be mad at me unless I go and find it out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing. We can't switch our cell phones on in here, so Misa-Misa has to come all the way here, just to see Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, hurry up and go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't keep a lady waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk! {\alpha&HFF&}Why is he with Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk! Why is he with Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's lifespan has halved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely she didn't trade eyes with Ryuk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-{\alpha&HFF&}Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, {\alpha&HFF&}no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But I traded eyes with Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I traded eyes with Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all going according to plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! {\alpha&HFF&}That means your lifespan has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! That means your lifespan has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}I want to be with you in an ideal world for as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, I want to be with you in an ideal world for as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way I feel, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}let's build a new world together... a world without criminals, filled only with kind-hearted people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, let's build a new world together... {\alpha&HFF&}a world without criminals, filled only with kind-hearted people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, let's build a new world together... a world without criminals, filled only with kind-hearted people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.24,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(564,295)}To be continued
